text: The fifth series of I'm a Celebrity...Get Me Out of Here! began on 20 November 2005 and ended on 5 December 2005. The programme ran for 16 days (18 days if counting the day the celebrities arrived and the morning the finalists exited). The series was won by Carol Thatcher. ==Contestants== 12 contestants participated, one more than in the previous series. {| class=wikitable sortable" style="text-align: center; white-space:nowrap; margin:auto; font- size:95.2%;" |- !
